"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ariarne Titmus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ariarne_Titmus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ariarne_Titmus\"}, {\"begin\": 900, \"end\": 914, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_Australia\", \"score\": 0.9999999893998394, \"rank\": 1.0600090321180858e-08, \"text\": \"Team Australia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now just days after returning from Europe they are face-to-face with the reality of their Chelmer home finally no longer being theirs - after it fetched $2.41million in a deal sealed in the same week as the family celebrated parents Steve and Robyn's 28th wedding anniversary.\", \"from\": 990, \"to\": 1266, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1080, \"end\": 1087, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/River_Chelmer\", \"score\": 0.999776656690421, \"rank\": 0.00022339320277862886, \"text\": \"Chelmer\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/River_Chelmer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/River_Chelmer\"}, {\"begin\": 1233, \"end\": 1238, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robyn\", \"score\": 0.9999999962519723, \"rank\": 3.4332067010436974e-09, \"text\": \"Robyn\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robyn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robyn\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"What a fun time it has been,\\\" Mr Titmus said.\", \"from\": 1268, \"to\": 1314, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1302, \"end\": 1308, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Titmus\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Titmus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Titmus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Titmus\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ariarne Titmus and her sister Mia.\", \"from\": 1316, \"to\": 1350, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1316, \"end\": 1330, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ariarne_Titmus\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ariarne Titmus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ariarne_Titmus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ariarne_Titmus\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Picture: Instagram  \\\"For 28 years Queen Robyn has put up with me and says she wants to go again.\", \"from\": 1351, \"to\": 1447, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She is a powerhouse of a best friend, soul mate and wife.\", \"from\": 1448, \"to\": 1505, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When on a good thing stick to it.\\\"\", \"from\": 1506, \"to\": 1540, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have done so much and time has flown.\", \"from\": 1542, \"to\": 1583, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Raised two incredible young women, seen much of the world and made the simple moments in life extra special.\", \"from\": 1584, \"to\": 1692, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Can not wait to see what the future brings.\\\"\", \"from\": 1693, \"to\": 1737, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Athletes Lani Pallister, Noemi Fox, Ariarne Titmus, and Jessica Fox arriving back in Australia.\", \"from\": 1739, \"to\": 1834, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1748, \"end\": 1762, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lani_Pallister\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lani Pallister\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lani_Pallister\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lani_Pallister\"}, {\"begin\": 1764, \"end\": 1769, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noemi_(singer)\", \"score\": 0.9602690196202718, \"rank\": 0.031203120312036276, \"text\": \"Noemi\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q1